    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_63_22783-22821",
      "chapterUid": 63,
      "range": "22783-22821",
      "markText": "“秋风清，秋月明；落叶聚还散，寒鸦栖复惊。相思相见知何日，此时此夜难为情。”",
      "totalCount": 2680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=63&rangeStart=22783&rangeEnd=22821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=63&rangeStart=22783&rangeEnd=22821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_55_32743-32776",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "32743-32776",
      "markText": "你瞧这些白云聚了又散，散了又聚，人生离合，亦复如斯。你又何必烦恼？",
      "totalCount": 2584,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=32743&rangeEnd=32776",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=32743&rangeEnd=32776"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_62_31590-31650",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "31590-31650",
      "markText": "杨过急忙还礼，说道：“芙妹，咱俩从小一起长大，虽然常闹别扭，其实情若兄妹。只要你此后不再讨厌我、恨我，我就心满意足了。”",
      "totalCount": 2520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=31590&rangeEnd=31650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=31590&rangeEnd=31650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_27_3286-3320",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "3286-3320",
      "markText": "小龙女摇了摇头，说道：“我自己要嫁给过儿做妻子，他不会娶你女儿的。”",
      "totalCount": 2176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=3286&rangeEnd=3320",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=3286&rangeEnd=3320"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_46_693-789",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "693-789",
      "markText": "大声说道：“什么师徒名分，什么名节清白，咱们通通当是放屁！通通滚他妈的蛋！死也罢，活也罢，咱俩谁也没命苦，谁也不会孤苦伶仃。从今而后，你不是我师父，不是我姑姑，是我媳妇！是我妻子！是我老婆！”",
      "totalCount": 1972,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=693&rangeEnd=789",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=693&rangeEnd=789"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_31_18864-18937",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "18864-18937",
      "markText": "小龙女对杨过凝视半晌，突然“嘤”的一声，投入他怀中。杨过将她紧紧抱住，在她嘴上亲去。小龙女在他一吻之下，心魂俱醉，双手伸出去搂住他头颈，凑嘴回吻。",
      "totalCount": 1890,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=18864&rangeEnd=18937",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=18864&rangeEnd=18937"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_47_26717-26749",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "26717-26749",
      "markText": "小龙女叹道：“咱们不幸，那是命苦，让别人快快乐乐的，不很好吗？”",
      "totalCount": 1820,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=26717&rangeEnd=26749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=26717&rangeEnd=26749"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_12_14619-14646",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "14619-14646",
      "markText": "郭靖心中却道：“那又何足为奇？我那蓉儿自然胜她百倍。”",
      "totalCount": 1794,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=14619&rangeEnd=14646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=14619&rangeEnd=14646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_24_21022-21062",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "21022-21062",
      "markText": "黄蓉平素极少见他如此气恼，低声劝道：“靖哥哥，这孩子本性不好，犯不着为他生气。”",
      "totalCount": 1656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21022&rangeEnd=21062",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=21022&rangeEnd=21062"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_47_22337-22407",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "22337-22407",
      "markText": "郭芙怒道：“啊哟，好大的架子啊。难道我是存心来害你们的吗？我向你们赔了不是，也就是了，怎么发这般大脾气？小小一两枚针儿，又有什么了不起啦？”",
      "totalCount": 1620,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=22337&rangeEnd=22407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=22337&rangeEnd=22407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_55_34821-34904",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "34821-34904",
      "markText": "行了十余里，杨过骤然间心中一动：“雕兄寿高通灵，莫非它引我到南海去和龙儿相会么？”想到此处，胸口热血奔腾，难以抑止，迈开大步，随着神雕疾驰。只两个月间，已抵东海之滨。",
      "totalCount": 1584,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=34821&rangeEnd=34904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=34821&rangeEnd=34904"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_48_21246-21332",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "21246-21332",
      "markText": "唰的一响，郭芙长剑从鞘中抽出了一半，说道：“他的手臂便是我斩断的。我赔不是也赔过了，给爹爹妈妈也责罚过了，你们还在背后这般恶毒的骂我……”说到这里，眼眶一红，心中委屈无限。",
      "totalCount": 1580,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=21246&rangeEnd=21332",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=21246&rangeEnd=21332"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_40_25020-25109",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "25020-25109",
      "markText": "杨过素来与郭芙不睦，但对怀中这个幼女心头忽起异样之感：“我此刻为她死拼，若天幸救得她性命，七日之后我便死了，日后她长到她姊姊那般年纪，不知可会记得我否？”心头一酸，险些掉下泪来。",
      "totalCount": 1551,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=25020&rangeEnd=25109",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=25020&rangeEnd=25109"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_40_11707-11775",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "11707-11775",
      "markText": "郭靖脸色微变，顺手一拉黄蓉，想将她藏于自己身后。黄蓉低声道：“靖哥哥，襄阳城要紧，还是你我的情爱要紧？是你身子要紧，还是我的身子要紧？”",
      "totalCount": 1548,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=11707&rangeEnd=11775",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=11707&rangeEnd=11775"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_11_3194-3208",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3194-3208",
      "markText": "郭芙一楞，还没决定哭是不哭。",
      "totalCount": 1495,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932431&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3194&rangeEnd=3208",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/381329505e3a4f3819e01e4?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3194&rangeEnd=3208"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932431_55_26027-26108",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "26027-26108",
      "markText": "”杨过一回头，猛见崖壁上用剑尖刻着两行字，一行大的写道：“十六年后，在此重会，夫妻情深，勿失信约。”另一行较小的字写道：“小龙女嘱夫君杨郎，珍重万千，务求相聚。”",
